# CODEOWNERS — per-subtree ownership
#
# Order matters: the LAST matching pattern takes precedence.
# Each line specifies: <pattern> <owner1> [owner2 ...]
#
# At MVP stage there is a single maintainer (@BinHsu). As the team grows,
# expand this file to reflect per-area ownership (e.g., @eng-cpp for
# engine_cpp/, @eng-infra for deploy/).

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Default catch-all — every file not otherwise claimed
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
*                                           @BinHsu

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Architecture-critical files: changes here require maintainer review
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
