/SECURITY.md                                @BinHsu
/README.md                                  @BinHsu
/CONTRIBUTING.md                            @BinHsu
/LICENSE                                    @BinHsu

# Architecture Decision Records — never modified in place, only superseded
/docs/adr/                                  @BinHsu
/docs/threat-model.md                       @BinHsu
/docs/github-setup.md                       @BinHsu

